<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>生日快乐</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff6347;
            font-size: 3em;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #2f4f4f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>生日快乐！</h1>
    <p>亲爱的董医生，愿你的生日充满欢乐和惊喜！</p>
</body>

<script>
    window.onload = function() {
        var currentDate = new Date();
        document.getElementById("date").innerHTML = "今天是" + currentDate.getFullYear() + "年" + (currentDate.getMonth() + 1) + "月" + currentDate.getDate() + "日";
    };
</script>
<p id="date"></p>
</html>